flowchart TD
    APP[React 18 + Vite app] --> ROUTES[Application routes<br/>Dashboard, workflow editor, docs, auth surfaces]
    ROUTES --> CANVAS[Workflow canvas<br/>Nodes, edges, layout, selection]
    CANVAS --> PROPS[Properties panel<br/>Schema-driven fields, AI editor, docs panel]
